title: Photos: Charlie Strong gets lifted up by team, wears Golden Hat; Longhorns celebrate with fans
text: Texas Longhorns head coach Charlie Strong is lifted by his players after beating the Oklahoma Sooners after an NCAA football game between Oklahoma and Texas at the Cotton Bowl in Dallas Saturday October 10, 2015. Texas Longhorns beat Oklahoma Sooners 24-17. (Andy Jacobsohn/The Dallas Morning News)
